Paper: hep-th/0107078

Date: 2001-07-10

Title: Path Integral Formulation of Noncommutative Quantum Mechanics

Authors: Ciprian Acatrinei

Comments: Latex, 7 pages

Journal-ref: JHEP 0109 (2001) 007

We propose a phase-space path integral formulation of noncommutative quantummechanics, and prove its equivalence to the operatorial formulation. As anillustration, the partition function of a noncommutative two-dimensionalharmonic oscillator is calculated.